\pard\f0\fs28\qc {\b   3.            Blackstonia }               Hudson
\par

\pard\f0\fs24\qc By †T.G. Tutin.
\par

\par

\pard\f0\fs28 Annual herbs. Calyx deeply divided into 6-12 lobes. Corolla rotate, yellow; tube short; lobes 6-12. Anthers basifixed, oblong to linear, not or scarcely twisting spirally after dehiscence. Style filiform, caducous; stigma 2-lobed.
\par

